	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have continued to expand your base of knowledge at a breakneck pace, learning more and more and become ever more capable of anticipating future needs. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Constitution, Intelligence, or Charisma increases by +1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with a total of 2 skills, languages, and/or tools you are not proficient with.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die with a skill you are proficient with. The maximum expertise die for the chosen skill becomes a d12.</p></li><li><p>When you use @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.jet01i63abb2v66h]{Measure Twice, Cut Once}, make an Intelligence save with a DC of 25. On a success, your use of the feature is refunded. You can only benefit from this refund once per level (or once per long rest at scholar level 20).</p></li></ul>",
